import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Box, Grid, Card, CardContent, CardMedia, Button } from '@mui/material';
import backgroundImage from '../../Multimedia/Pictures/Coach_A.jpg';

const Trainers = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        backgroundImage: `url(${backgroundImage})`,
        backgroundSize: 'cover',
        backgroundPosition: 'center',
        backgroundAttachment: 'fixed',
        minHeight: '100vh',
        pt: 4,
        pb: 6,
        '&::before': {
          content: '""',
          position: 'fixed',
          top: 0,
          left: 0,
          right: 0,
          bottom: 0,
          backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)',
          zIndex: 1,
        },
      }}
    >
      <Container sx={{ position: 'relative', zIndex: 2 }}>
        <Box
          sx={{
            backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)',
            padding: 4,
            borderRadius: 2,
            marginBottom: 4,
          }}
        >
          <Typography
            variant="h2"
            component="h1"
            gutterBottom
            sx={{
              color: '#FFFFFF',
              textAlign: 'center',
              fontWeight: 'bold',
              textTransform: 'uppercase',
            }}
          >
            Our Elite Trainers
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="h5"
            sx={{
              color: '#FFFFFF',
              textAlign: 'center',
              mb: 4,
            }}
          >
            Transform your life with Africa's finest fitness experts
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/400x300/?african,trainer"
                alt="Trainer 1"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                  John Doe
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666', mb: 2 }}>
                  Specializes in strength training and muscle building
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  fullWidth
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
                    '&:hover': {
                      backgroundColor: '#CC0000',
                    },
                  }}
                  href="/booking"
                >
                  Book Session
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/400x300/?african,fitness,woman"
                alt="Trainer 2"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                  Sarah Johnson
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666', mb: 2 }}>
                  Expert in HIIT and cardio workouts
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  fullWidth
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
                    '&:hover': {
                      backgroundColor: '#CC0000',
                    },
                  }}
                  href="/booking"
                >
                  Book Session
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9)' }}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="300"
                image="https://source.unsplash.com/random/400x300/?african,gym"
                alt="Trainer 3"
              />
              <CardContent>
                <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="h2" sx={{ color: '#000000' }}>
                  Michael Smith
                </Typography>
                <Typography sx={{ color: '#666666', mb: 2 }}>
                  Specialized in weight loss and nutrition planning
                </Typography>
                <Button
                  variant="contained"
                  fullWidth
                  sx={{
                    backgroundColor: '#FF0000',
                    '&:hover': {
                      backgroundColor: '#CC0000',
                    },
                  }}
                  href="/booking"
                >
                  Book Session
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Trainers;
